web_form_fields.label: Inspect the machine for transit damages & convey to the factory (if any)
Check all packing boxes as per the packing list.
Check the machine positioning. Keep 1MTR space from all side for easy maintenance.
Fill Hydraulic oil (Grade As Per Pump Required)
Check tightness of Stationary Platen & Guide rod support bolts.
Fit & align Clamping side & Injection side L.T.'s
Check all covers for proper matching with each other.
Check the actuation of limit switches & Hydraulic safety lever with door movement.
Fit the hopper assembly on barrel platen.
Check if any short supplied material & convey to the factory.
Level the machine with in 0.06mm / Meter Across & along the tiebar (Parallel)
Remove the grease applied on tiebars, Cross head guide rod, Base frame pads, Toggle link in case of oil lubrication system.
Check for proper lubricants for respective assemblies 00 grade grease for Clamping unit Mobil 222 grease for transmission shaft assly.
Check smooth movement of the front & rear door.
Check barrel throat for foreign material.
Back up Fuses for incoming supply
Check 24 v across both SMPS (If the voltage found disturbed then adjust it by using POT provided on SMPS.
Check all thermocouple are secured in their holders.
Check all machine operations in manual mode.
Check machine operations in semi & auto mode.
Check earth & 99 ( DC -ve ) wires are separated.
Check linearization of L.T.'s. (If required, adjusted the same. Update the same in customer's machine history file & convey to H.O.) .
Check Optional features required by the customer are in proper working condition.
